    "content": "<h1 dir=\"auto\">Xiaomi RearScreen Music</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p dir=\"auto\">About: A music player compatible with the Xiaomi RearScreen series.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><em><a href=\"README.md\">English</a> | <a href=\"README_zh.md\">简体中文</a></em></p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">A highly dynamic, elegantly designed music player widget custom-built for Xiaomi devices equipped with a rear screen. It leverages HyperOS/MIUI widget capabilities to deliver a seamless, native-feeling audio control experience.</p>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">✨ Features</h3>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li><strong>Dynamic Lyric Animations</strong>: Lyrics slide up smoothly with a custom transition effect whenever the track progresses, without visual stuttering.</li>\n<li><strong>HyperMaterial &amp; Adaptive Colors</strong>: Automatically extracts color palettes from the current album art to tint the background and UI elements, creating an immersive visual experience.</li>\n<li><strong>Always-On Display (AOD) Support</strong>: Seamlessly transitions between active screen and AOD states, rearranging the layout (like artist and title) to save power while keeping information visible.</li>\n<li><strong>Full Media Controls</strong>: Easily play, pause, skip, or go back to previous tracks with smooth Lottie icon animations.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">🛠 Contributing</h3>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Contributions, issues, and feature requests are welcome! Feel free to check the <a href=\"../../issues\">issues page</a>.</p>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">📄 License</h3>\n<p dir=\"auto\">This project is licensed under the <a href=\"LICENSE\">GPL-3.0 License</a>.</p>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Star History</h2>\n<a href=\"https://www.star-history.com/?repos=SiberiaApp%2FXiaomi-RearScreen-Music&amp;type=date&amp;legend=top-left\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n <themed-picture data-catalyst-inline=\"true\"><picture>\n   <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/628c731fc8fea4e48f31cf0f67cea2ca3eb4c8